    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs(wp.cos((v0 + 0.83 + tmp + 0.67)))
    tmp = wp.cos(((tmp + 0.56 - v0 + 0.96) / wp.cos(v1 + 0.61)))
    v2 = wp.sin((0.89 + (v0 + 0.02 / tmp + 0.44)))
    tmp = 0.27
    v1 = wp.exp(tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
